divs: Sighting Details"Narrative below was submitted by MUFON Dispatch for witness based on phone conversation with witness". At approximately 1:25am I went outside and saw a flash of light near an aircraft in the clear night time sky. I could see a pink star with the naked eye. I looked through my binoculars and could see a craft with blue-white spinning lights under the craft. It was traveling then stopped, then started traveling again. I felt there was telepathic communication with the occupants.
